  <IdeoDiversity_Abhorrent.comps.5.thoughtStageDescriptions.0>محيط موحد</IdeoDiversity_Abhorrent.comps.5.thoughtStageDescriptions.0>
  <!-- EN: Diverse surroundings -->
  <IdeoDiversity_Abhorrent.comps.5.thoughtStageDescriptions.1>محيط متنوع</IdeoDiversity_Abhorrent.comps.5.thoughtStageDescriptions.1>
  
